\newlabel{lst:rmsnorm}{{5.1}{26}{\texttt {rmsnorm<S>} implementation from \texttt {forward.h}. Data is staged into local buffers before computation so that \texttt {ARRAY\_PARTITION} can be applied. The reduction loop uses \texttt {UNROLL factor=4} to accumulate four partial sums simultaneously. The normalisation loop uses \texttt {UNROLL factor=64} since it is fully data-parallel}{lstlisting.71}{}}
