\newlabel{lst:matmul_update3}{{5.8}{52}{Core tile loop structure of the tiled \texttt {matmul<N,D>} from \texttt {FFN\_update3.h}. Each tile loads \texttt {TILE\_D\,=\,4} weight rows via \texttt {memcpy} bursts (Phase 1), computes \texttt {TILE\_D} dot products from BRAM (Phase 2), and writes results (Phase 3). The \texttt {dot\_inner} unroll factor matches \texttt {PARALLEL\_MACS\,=\,16}}{lstlisting.295}{}}
\newlabel{lst:matmul_update3@cref}{{[listing][8][5]5.8}{[1][52][]52}{}{}{}}
